    {
      "line": 373,
      "term": "tools",
      "snippet": "His is a dictionary of both words and ideas. It works to reveal the cultural blinders with which we experience the world. Only 16 of the 170 untranslatable words in Howard’s forthcoming book, They Have a Word For It, are excerpted here. (It'll be out in March 1988 from Jeremy P. Tarcher, Inc.) Howard is also author of three other books: Tools For Thought (Prentice- - Hall, 1986), The Cognitive Connection (Prentice-Hall, 1987), and Higher Creativity (J. P. Tarcher, 1984). -Jeanne Carstensen Angeles. To be published in March 1988. 27 GATE FIVE ROAD SAUSALITO, CA 94965 3"
